接口 Navigator

    Frederik Heremans

    • 方法详细资料

      • getTrigger

        String getTrigger()
        Gets the string that triggers this handler to be used when navigation should be performed. This is the first part of the uri-fragment.

      • handleNavigation

        void handleNavigation(UriFragment uriFragment)
        Handle the incoming navigation request. The url-fragment passed contains all uri parts that triggered the navigation request (including the one returned by getTrigger()), as well as the parameters contain the values of the parameters passed in the query string (if any). The handleNavigation is responsible for setting the current URI-fragment to the correct value (the passed uriFragment or another on in case URL is invalid).
